song_lyrics: Japat nām nar pātkī hot hai pūran kām...
Bhuvi rajkan kou gine barkhā bund gināy,
Tārankī ginatī kare pan Harigun gineu na jāy... gun 1
Charitra kiye Mahārājne avni upar āy,
Likhte hārī shārdā sahasra badan nit gāy... gun 2
Chyār baran āshram chau pashu pakshī parjant,
Bhut pret ādi sabe tāre jīva anant... gun 3
Daras paras deke Hari fal jal patra le hār,
Premānand kiye Nāthne anant jīva bhavpār... gun 4
title: Gunsāgar Ghanshyāmjī sukhsāgar jehī nām
